{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901",
    "name": "Baby Go — Payments (Cliente)",
    "description": "Pagos Stripe — contexto cliente.\n\nModelo marketplace: el pago va a la cuenta plataforma y al completar el servicio se transfiere al provider.\n\nVariables:\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:3000/api\n- `token`: JWT del cliente\n- `storeId`: store donde se alquila\n- `paymentId`: id del pago (tras crear PaymentIntent)\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Provider completa Stripe Connect (colección Provider Store → 7b/7c)\n2. POST Crear PaymentIntent → copiar `payment.id` a `paymentId`\n3. POST Confirmar pago (dev) → status `succeeded` (en app real: clientSecret + Stripe.js)\n4. POST Transferir al provider (fin del alquiler)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "storeId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Payments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Crear PaymentIntent",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"storeId\": \"{{storeId}}\",\n  \"amount\": 10000,\n  \"orderId\": \"order-demo-001\",\n  \"currency\": \"eur\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments"]
            },
            "description": "Crea PaymentIntent en cuenta plataforma. Respuesta: `clientSecret`, `publishableKey`, `payment`. Copiá `payment.id` → variable `paymentId`. Monto en centavos (10000 = €100.00)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Consultar pago",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "{{paymentId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Estado del pago: requires_payment_method, succeeded, transferred, etc."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2b. Confirmar pago (solo dev/test)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}/confirm-test",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "{{paymentId}}", "confirm-test"]
            },
            "description": "Simula el cobro con tarjeta test `pm_card_visa`. Solo funciona fuera de production.\n\nDespués de esto, `status` debe ser `succeeded` y podés ejecutar el paso 3 (transfer)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Transferir al provider (servicio completado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}/transfer",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "{{paymentId}}", "transfer"]
            },
            "description": "Cuando el alquiler finaliza: transfiere `providerAmount` al connected account de la store. Requiere status `succeeded`. La comisión plataforma queda en cuenta empresa."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks (referencia)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Stripe webhook (solo Stripe CLI)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "stripe-signature",
                "value": "{{stripeSignature}}",
                "description": "Generado por Stripe CLI — no manual"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/stripe",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks", "stripe"]
            },
            "description": "No probar manualmente en Postman. Usar Stripe CLI:\n\nstripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/api/webhooks/stripe\n\nCopiar el whsec_... a STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET en .env"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
